   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>" ...................................................................................... When the peasants found you in the monastery with the priest Jakob, you (?) said to them: "Our father will send after the camels and fetch them (?)." Now behold the peasants have come north and have said to the people of the village: "Remove (?) the camels south." Behold the people of the village have said to us: "If the camels eat (?) in our field, and we flee to the place of all the . . . . . . . . .  of Egypt, then you have them taken south." But now, if it is the idea to take them south, then send the man for us by the 1st of Tobe. Salvation in the Lord!"</ab>
         </div>
